  • Deprecated Methods
  • Deprecated Classes 
    Class and Description
    org.bytedeco.tensorrt.nvinfer.DimsCHW
    DimsCHW will be removed in TensorRT 8.0, use Dims3 instead.
    org.bytedeco.tensorrt.nvinfer.DimsNCHW
    DimsNCHW will be removed in TensorRT 8.0, use Dims4 instead.
    org.bytedeco.tensorrt.nvinfer.IOutputDimensionsFormula
    IOutputDimensionsFormula has been superseded by PaddingMode and will be removed in TensorRT 9.0.
    org.bytedeco.tensorrt.nvinfer.IPluginLayer
    This interface is superseded by IPluginV2Layer and will be removed in TensorRT 8.0. \warning Do not inherit from this class, as doing so will break forward-compatibility of the API and ABI.
    org.bytedeco.tensorrt.nvinfer.IRNNLayer
    This interface is superseded by IRNNv2Layer and will be removed in TensorRT 8.0. \warning Do not inherit from this class, as doing so will break forward-compatibility of the API and ABI.
    org.bytedeco.tensorrt.nvinfer.IRNNv2Layer
    IRNNv2Layer will be removed in TensorRT 9.0, use ILoop::addLoop instead. \warning Do not inherit from this class, as doing so will break forward-compatibility of the API and ABI.
    org.bytedeco.tensorrt.nvinfer_plugin.softmaxTree
    . This plugin is superseded by createRegionPlugin and will be removed in TensorRT 8.0.
